@startuml embedder
!include ../_includes/style.iuml
!include ../_includes/actors.iuml

title Embedder — managed lifecycle (slice 7e)

package "src/main/modelhub/" {
  component "embedderLifecycle.ts\n• ensureEmbedderReady(filePath)\n• in-flight launch promise\n  (concurrency-safe)\n• stopManagedEmbedders()" as EMBED_LC
  component "launchModelByPath\n(via launch.ts)\nlaunchedBy: 'embedder'\ncustomArgs: '--embedding'" as LAUNCH
  component "EmbedClient\n(routing/embed.ts)\n/v1/embeddings POST" as EMBED_CLIENT
  component "routingConfig.ts\n.routingEmbedderPath /\n.routingEmbedderBaseUrl" as RC
}

component "characterizeRunner\n(slice 7c probe)" as CHARACT
component "routeByVectors\n(slice 5b query path)" as ROUTE

CHARACT --> RC : effectiveRoutingParams\n.embedder
ROUTE --> RC : same
RC --> EMBED_LC : kind:'managed'\n+ filePath
RC ..> EMBED_CLIENT : kind:'external'\n+ baseUrl (direct)
EMBED_LC --> LAUNCH : spawn if not running
LAUNCH --> LLAMA_EMBED : llama-server\n--embedding
LLAMA_EMBED --> EMBED_LC : /v1/models OK\n(ready probe, 60s timeout)
EMBED_LC --> EMBED_CLIENT : baseUrl
EMBED_CLIENT --> LLAMA_EMBED : POST /v1/embeddings

note bottom of EMBED_LC
  Idempotent: existing process
  with `launchedBy: 'embedder'`
  is reused. Concurrent callers
  share the same launch promise.
  Boot crash ⇒ stopProcess + return
  null (silent fallback to R5).
end note

note right of LLAMA_EMBED
  Visible in RunningModelsPanel
  grouped by `launchedBy: 'embedder'`
  alongside chat models.
end note

@enduml
